adela is a 2008 filipino drama independent film starring the philippine screen legend , anita linda . the film was a tribute for the award-winning film veteran which won best actress awards from the gawad tanglaw , 10th cinemanila international film festival ( southeast asia film competition ) and young critics circle for her portrayal of the titular character . the story of adela , which takes place in a span of one day , is a heartbreaking story of a woman who longs for the company of her loved ones . some of the stars tapped to act as adela 's neighbors are jason abalos , angeli bayani , and iza calzado .